<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 20:06:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列MK呼吁西方“欢迎”来自加沙的难民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/israeli-mks-publish-plan-to-transfer-gazans-to-europe-to-alleviate-humanitarian-crisis/0000018b-ce7c-d168-a3ef-dffeed320000</link><description>在《华尔街日报》的一篇文章中，来自联盟和反对派的两位议员表示，将数万名加沙人转移到欧洲是对加沙人民表现出同情心的“道义责任和机会”。极右翼部长斯莫特里奇和本格维尔很快表示支持</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 16:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/israeli-mks-publish-plan-to-transfer-gazans-to-europe-to-alleviate-humanitarian-crisis/0000018b-ce7c-d168-a3ef-dffeed320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列俘虏家属对政府越来越不耐烦，开始为期五天的游行前往耶路撒冷，要求立即解决人质问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-set-out-on-5-day-march-to-jlem-to-demand-hostage-deal/0000018b-ce70-dffa-adef-ee7096200000</link><description>随着时间的推移，这些家庭的语气明显变得更加尖锐，因为他们看到并担心军事目标和外交利益被优先考虑到他们认为政府的首要责任——让亲人回家</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 16:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-set-out-on-5-day-march-to-jlem-to-demand-hostage-deal/0000018b-ce70-dffa-adef-ee7096200000</guid></item><item><title>“类似于病毒”：虚假信息成为以色列与哈马斯战争致命的新战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/similar-to-a-virus-disinformation-becomes-deadly-new-front-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-cde9-dd11-a19f-edfd51180000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯之间在传统媒体和社交媒体上就 10 月 7 日大屠杀和随后的战争展开的斗争不仅是为了影响公众舆论，也是为了在新闻报道本身中播下不信任的种子</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 15:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/similar-to-a-virus-disinformation-becomes-deadly-new-front-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-cde9-dd11-a19f-edfd51180000</guid></item><item><title>“利用犹太人的痛苦”：欧洲极右翼如何利用犹太人、穆斯林和加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-jewish-pain-how-europes-far-right-is-exploiting-jews-muslims-and-the-gaza-war/0000018b-ca31-dd30-a5ff-eff10c840000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯之间的战争已经过去一个多月了，极右翼欧洲政党正在寻找机会将自己定位为犹太社区的朋友，同时谴责穆斯林移民的“危险”。政治学家表示这种拥抱不会持续太久</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 14:20:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-jewish-pain-how-europes-far-right-is-exploiting-jews-muslims-and-the-gaza-war/0000018b-ca31-dd30-a5ff-eff10c840000</guid></item><item><title>为什么 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中残酷的性暴力被忽视？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-14/ty-article-podcast/why-is-the-cruel-sexual-violence-of-the-october-7-hamas-attack-being-ignored/0000018b-cdbe-d423-affb-ffbfe0d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 13:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-14/ty-article-podcast/why-is-the-cruel-sexual-violence-of-the-october-7-hamas-attack-being-ignored/0000018b-cdbe-d423-affb-ffbfe0d20000</guid></item><item><title>前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾在激烈的电视对峙中拒绝称哈马斯为恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/jeremy-corbyn-refuses-to-call-hamas-a-terror-organization-in-heated-tv-standoff/0000018b-cdd6-df9a-ab8b-dfde64960000</link><description>这位长期受到反犹太主义指控的前英国工党党魁在出现在皮尔斯·摩根的节目中时回避了有关哈马斯恐怖组织地位的 15 个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 13:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/jeremy-corbyn-refuses-to-call-hamas-a-terror-organization-in-heated-tv-standoff/0000018b-cdd6-df9a-ab8b-dfde64960000</guid></item><item><title>“我们有 83 个早产儿。他们会死”：以色列必须重新考虑袭击希法医院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-have-83-premature-babies-they-will-die-israel-must-rethink-attacking-al-shifa/0000018b-cdc8-d423-affb-ffeb9bdd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 13:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-have-83-premature-babies-they-will-die-israel-must-rethink-attacking-al-shifa/0000018b-cdc8-d423-affb-ffeb9bdd0000</guid></item><item><title>音乐变成枪声之前的那一刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/drawing-the-moment-before-the-music-turned-to-gunfire/0000018b-cd2e-d518-a39b-ff3f91c20000</link><description>艺术家 Andres Gurwicz 使用毛笔根据 Nova 音乐节创作作品，该音乐节在 10 月 7 日变成了残酷屠杀和酷刑的场所</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/drawing-the-moment-before-the-music-turned-to-gunfire/0000018b-cd2e-d518-a39b-ff3f91c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸城市图尔卡尔姆开火，造成七名巴勒斯坦人死亡，三人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-three-critically-wounded-by-israeli-fire-in-west-bank-city/0000018b-cd9c-d423-affb-ffbfdfd90000</link><description>除了以色列国防军在图尔卡姆 (Tul Karm) 无人机袭击造成的伤亡之外，希伯伦附近的一名 20 岁巴勒斯坦男子在一名士兵附近拔出一把刀后被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-three-critically-wounded-by-israeli-fire-in-west-bank-city/0000018b-cd9c-d423-affb-ffbfdfd90000</guid></item><item><title>民调显示，随着战争愈演愈烈，以色列人对内塔尼亚胡的信任度直线下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/as-war-rages-israelis-trust-in-netanyahu-hits-rock-bottom-polls-find/0000018b-cd86-dd11-a19f-edf6f2b00000</link><description>巴伊兰大学研究人员进行的一项民意调查询问以色列人对加沙战争信息和决策的信任程度。结果显示，不到 4% 的人信任内塔尼亚胡；以色列国防军发言人哈加里被评为“最可靠”人物</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:05:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/as-war-rages-israelis-trust-in-netanyahu-hits-rock-bottom-polls-find/0000018b-cd86-dd11-a19f-edf6f2b00000</guid></item><item><title>伊恩·布雷默：“内塔尼亚胡的自恋极大地伤害了以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ian-bremmer-netanyahus-narcissism-has-greatly-harmed-israel/0000018b-b4e8-d3c1-a39b-bee980d20000</link><description>战略专家伊恩·布雷默认为，尽管哈马斯的残酷袭击造成了创伤，但加沙战争不会危及以色列的存在。他还指出了如果地面战争持续太久的风险</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:04:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ian-bremmer-netanyahus-narcissism-has-greatly-harmed-israel/0000018b-b4e8-d3c1-a39b-bee980d20000</guid></item><item><title>研究表明鞋子可能早在 15 万年前就已经出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-14/ty-article/shoes-could-have-emerged-as-much-as-150-000-years-ago-study-suggests/0000018b-cd6d-df9a-ab8b-dfed4d440000</link><description>中石器时代南非岩石海滩上没有脚趾印的脚印可能表明有人穿着鞋子</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:39:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-14/ty-article/shoes-could-have-emerged-as-much-as-150-000-years-ago-study-suggests/0000018b-cd6d-df9a-ab8b-dfed4d440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争正在扰乱英国政坛。它会决定下次选举吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-is-rattling-british-politics-will-it-decide-the-next-election/0000018b-c983-d993-a1bb-f99fcf9a0000</link><description>在大规模亲巴勒斯坦集会、极右机会主义、科尔宾主义辩护以及英国反犹太主义呈指数级增长的背景下，执政的保守党和反对党工党都在以色列-加沙战争的政治风暴中航行。随着大选的临近，赌注异常高</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-is-rattling-british-politics-will-it-decide-the-next-election/0000018b-c983-d993-a1bb-f99fcf9a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在华盛顿集会人数创历史新高，支持以色列对哈马斯的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/record-number-of-u-s-jews-to-rally-in-d-c-in-show-of-support-for-israels-war-on-hamas/0000018b-cd27-dd11-a19f-edf7b4350000</link><description>随着以色列-加沙战争接近第 40 天，超过 20 万人参加了在华盛顿国家广场举行的活动。参与者包括民主党政治家、福音派领袖和以色列流行歌星</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:59:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/record-number-of-u-s-jews-to-rally-in-d-c-in-show-of-support-for-israels-war-on-hamas/0000018b-cd27-dd11-a19f-edf7b4350000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的记者争先恐后地记录以色列的轰炸。数十人付出了生命的代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-journalist-rush-to-document-israeli-bombardments-dozens-have-paid-with-their-lives/0000018b-cd06-d423-affb-ffa7e85d0000</link><description>许多人还失去了家人，家园遭到破坏或毁坏，办公室也遭到袭击。随着破坏的加剧，越来越多的报道是由普通人用即兴的方式进行的</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-journalist-rush-to-document-israeli-bombardments-dozens-have-paid-with-their-lives/0000018b-cd06-d423-affb-ffa7e85d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列狂欢大屠杀受害者因未完全皈依犹太教而被埋在墓地外</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/victim-of-rave-massacre-buried-outside-cemetery-due-to-incomplete-conversion-to-judaism/0000018b-cd3c-df9a-ab8b-dffccc370000</link><description>由于尚未完成皈依犹太教的课程，10 月 7 日在诺瓦音乐节上遇害的阿丽娜·法拉哈蒂 (Alina Falahati) 被拒绝埋葬在犹太公墓。以色列拉比官员表示，“这是一个错误”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/victim-of-rave-massacre-buried-outside-cemetery-due-to-incomplete-conversion-to-judaism/0000018b-cd3c-df9a-ab8b-dffccc370000</guid></item><item><title>加沙简史：五千年的冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-short-history-of-gaza-5-000-years-of-strife/0000017f-e4ae-d7b2-a77f-e7afb6a40000</link><description>正如先知所预言的那样，这片土地自古以来就一直在争夺</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-short-history-of-gaza-5-000-years-of-strife/0000017f-e4ae-d7b2-a77f-e7afb6a40000</guid></item><item><title>中国、伊朗和阿拉伯国家谴责以色列部长关于在加沙投放核弹的声明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/china-iran-arab-nations-condemn-israeli-ministers-nuclear-bomb-statement/0000018b-cce6-df9a-ab8b-deeeb98f0000</link><description>极右翼部长阿米猜·埃利亚胡在电台采访中的即兴评论引发了争议和国际关注。世界各地的官员称其“极其不负责任且令人不安”，“对地区稳定构成重大威胁”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 09:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/china-iran-arab-nations-condemn-israeli-ministers-nuclear-bomb-statement/0000018b-cce6-df9a-ab8b-deeeb98f0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示掌握哈马斯利用加沙医院进行军事活动并扣押人质的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-live/body-of-canadian-israel-peace-activist-idd-hamas-publishes-video-of-captive-idf-soldier/0000018b-cc03-d57d-afff-cff3a1f90000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军在约旦河西岸城市图尔卡姆的炮火造成七名巴勒斯坦人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军证实周一出现在哈马斯视频中的以色列士兵死亡 ■ 以色列国防军证实周一有两名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ MKs 呼吁将加沙人转移到其他国家《华尔街日报》中的国家 ■ 以色列国防部长加兰特：哈马斯已失去对加沙的控制 ■ 至少 1,200 名以色列人在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生，239 名人质在加沙被扣 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：自战争开始以来已有 11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 04:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-live/body-of-canadian-israel-peace-activist-idd-hamas-publishes-video-of-captive-idf-soldier/0000018b-cc03-d57d-afff-cff3a1f90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙取得进展，但哈马斯投降还远未到来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-is-making-headway-in-gaza-but-hamas-surrender-is-far-from-imminent/0000018b-ca6f-d8c7-a59b-df6f80560000</link><description>考虑到国际上的限制，以色列国防军的愿望可能无法实现，但对于加沙的以色列军官来说，只有击败哈马斯，行动才会结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 04:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-is-making-headway-in-gaza-but-hamas-surrender-is-far-from-imminent/0000018b-ca6f-d8c7-a59b-df6f80560000</guid></item></channel></rss>